(5, 66, 'Maria', 'john-nelson', '<p>I&nbsp;was labeled&nbsp;as a whore&nbsp;the day I told my family&nbsp;that I was with child. They&nbsp;turned&nbsp;their&nbsp;back on me ­ I stood&nbsp;there&nbsp;completely&nbsp;alone. The&nbsp;boy&nbsp;that&nbsp;I&nbsp;once&nbsp;felt&nbsp;for&nbsp;and&nbsp;who&nbsp;had&nbsp;pressured&nbsp;me&nbsp;into&nbsp;sex,&nbsp;also&nbsp;turned&nbsp;his back&nbsp;to&nbsp;me&nbsp;this&nbsp;day… I&nbsp;stood&nbsp;there&nbsp;without&nbsp;any&nbsp;support.</p>\r\n<p>The&nbsp;only&nbsp;way&nbsp;I&nbsp;could&nbsp;support&nbsp;myself&nbsp;and&nbsp;my&nbsp;child&nbsp;was&nbsp;to&nbsp;sell&nbsp;my&nbsp;body.&nbsp;This&nbsp;is&nbsp;not desirable,&nbsp;but&nbsp;I&nbsp;see&nbsp;no&nbsp;option&nbsp;right&nbsp;now,&nbsp;I&nbsp;want&nbsp;out&nbsp;of&nbsp;it,&nbsp;but&nbsp;who&nbsp;will&nbsp;hire&nbsp;a&nbsp;young single&nbsp;mother&nbsp;with&nbsp;no&nbsp;education?</p>\r\n<p>I&nbsp;try&nbsp;to&nbsp;bring&nbsp;in&nbsp;enough&nbsp;money&nbsp;to&nbsp;go&nbsp;to&nbsp;school.&nbsp;I&nbsp;only&nbsp;sell&nbsp;myself&nbsp;when&nbsp;there&nbsp;is&nbsp;no food&nbsp;for&nbsp;my&nbsp;son,&nbsp;I&nbsp;feel&nbsp;dirty&nbsp;and&nbsp;I&nbsp;feel&nbsp;unworthy, so&nbsp;school&nbsp;is&nbsp;out&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;question. I&nbsp;cry&nbsp;myself&nbsp;to&nbsp;sleep&nbsp;every&nbsp;night,&nbsp;but&nbsp;it&nbsp;pleases&nbsp;me&nbsp;that&nbsp;my&nbsp;son&nbsp;is&nbsp;healthy.&nbsp;That&nbsp;is what&nbsp;makes&nbsp;me&nbsp;continue.&nbsp;I&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;mocked&nbsp;and&nbsp;spat&nbsp;upon,&nbsp;while&nbsp;grossly&nbsp;utilized. I&nbsp;feel&nbsp;that&nbsp;I&nbsp;never&nbsp;can&nbsp;be&nbsp;washed&nbsp;clean&nbsp;enough&nbsp;from&nbsp;guilt&nbsp;and&nbsp;shame.&nbsp;And&nbsp;I&nbsp;will never&nbsp;ever&nbsp;let&nbsp;my&nbsp;son&nbsp;know&nbsp;what&nbsp;I&nbsp;am, a&nbsp;whore.</p>', '', 1, 9, '2014-06-01 17:58:13', 852, '', '2014-06-06 18:43:24', 852, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-01 17:58:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intr