(9, 75, 'Who we are', 'who-we-are', '<h4>Hearts for a New Life Foundation</h4>\r\n<p>Our mission is the achievement of integrated development of girls and children from economically disadvantaged backgrounds as well as that of parents and single mothers. We accomplish this through an education of quality and just treatment with lifestyle solutions and skills; respecting their rights, their diversity, their natural rhythm of growth and learning with a constant concern for the environment they live in; developing fundamental values integrating the family and community. We endeavor to support ​ in all these ways at the beginning stages of a new life, a life which can be filled with peace and happiness!</p>\r\n<p>This is most of all an Association for Young Mothers, but to help simply the individual is not enough. We believe to create lasting change in an often hostile setting, we must be prepared to help to heal the whole family.</p>\r\n<p>This is an Establishment for a NEW Beginning and a Conscious Upbringing.</p>\r\n<p>There is a vital need for support of young and single mothers in South America. Young girls are frequently forced to marry if they become pregnant with a child, often even if the pregnancy is a result of sexual abuse. Many young girls experience abuse by family members. Many run away from rape and incest and hide in the mountains.</p>\r\n<p>HFANL is here to help the young mothers and their children. We support them in a caring way with LOVE, education, food, shelter, medical care, support with needed legal action, therapy, paid work, and so much more. We help them to create a new start and a new life, the LIFE that they wish for themselves.</p>\r\n<p>First of ALL this is a powerful work of conveying FEELINGS… the feeling of the DIGNITY OF LIFE, the feeling of being LOVED, cared for, appreciated and for my Team and I to GIVE them back the feeling of LIFE! Their OWN LIFE!</p>\r\n<p>We help the young mothers to feel responsible for their children''s lives, to LOVE their children, even after their painful experiences. The main philosophy of the association is to train them to help themselves - to empower young single mothers to be able to take responsibility for their own and their children''s lives and provide for their families and futures.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4><br />General Information</h4>\r\n<p>Not everyone has the same opportunities to live a quality LIFE. Some never do, unless someone comes with a BIG warm Heart and an outstretched Hand, sharing insights on how to free themselves from a painful past to live a more worthwhile LIFE. This is why Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lionheart is the creator of Hearts For a New LIFE Foundation. Welcome to our site! We wish this work to INSPIRE and uplift YOU! This is an inclusive place with immense motivation where there is room for EVERY ONE who wishes to change their LIFE to the LIFE they want to Create!</p>', '', 1, 2, '2014-06-08 06:07:37', 852, '', '2014-06-08 16:00:12', 852, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-08 06:07:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 7, '', '', 1, 1563, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(10, 77, 'Projects', 'projects', '<h4>Mother Pearl´s Home</h4>\r\n<p>This project is aimed at social support in which institutional care for children, youth, pregnant women, single mothers, adults and older at risk adults, disadvantaged and/or abandoned individuals is offered exclusive priority, ensuring their protection and the defense of their rights. At Mother Pearl''s Home we always seek reintegration back into the family unit and the preservation of community.</p>\r\n<p>This work is located at "MOTHER PEARL''S HOME" in Malacatos, in the Parish of the Hearts for a new life Foundation led by its President Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lionheart of Norwegian nationality. Gifted with LOVE and Deeper understanding. Pearl is able to carry out this work with the sole purpose of helping vulnerable people in society, This assistance will be provided in a home group setting, supported financially by the Foundation and by both local and foreign volunteers from around the world.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>​Yunanga ​Corazon Cultural</h4>\r\n<p>Is our Educational offer for the poor Children of Malacatos who are not able to afford travel to the city of Loja for an education. This project is intended to promote and secure access to learning Music, Art, Culture, Nutrition, Color, Natural Medicine, Yoga, Meditation and more in the Parish of Malacatos Loja City. Yunanga Corazon Cultural is there for this sector of society educating the children in a way that is believed to be necessary for the growth and strengthening of values and morals through learning the arts instructing them with the affection and care that children deserve.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>This project will take place in the Yunanga Hotel in which we currently hold guitar lessons directed to children of Malacatos and surroundings, whose owner is Lord Nelson Medina, generously offering his beautiful property for this project.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>"Hearts Foundation for A New Life" led by its President Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lionheart, who with her wonderful gifts of knowledge and understanding and Vision intends this assistance to be provided for these vulnerable and neglected members of society. It is Pearl''s Personal and Team Vision that by running this project to build a foundation for future young artists and good people full of passion and love to enrich society and as a result, also the country at large.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Recycling - Therapy and Art!<br />Love the World</h4>\r\n<p>Some of the most wonderful things that this foundation focuses on lie in the activities in which the HFANL community transforms recycled items into ART! This project mostly reaches the Children in order create awareness, protect nature and to instill a creative intelligence and responsibility in young people. For example, working with cork is a soothing form of therapy, it is a natural, soft material giving an indescribable inner calm.</p>\r\n<p>One of the forms of therapy at "Mother Pearl''s Home" is recycling. Beginning with January 2015 we will start our project of transforming waste into the finest art as our Special Therapy. Working with wine corks is a great therapy for our patients, and especially for those patients who carry the negative memories associated with alcohol from their own childhood, abuse memories or being mistreated somehow when alcohol was involved . Pearl''s therapy method transforms trash (trauma and painful memories) into beautiful art and joy (liberation) - a NEW LIFE and a chance to start over. It''s about collaboration with the natural material of cork, and the human body . We will be working on many different Recycled projects such as Paper, glass bottles, water bottles and more.</p>\r\n<p>The greatest miracle on earth is our body. It contains infinite wisdom and vast resources that can, given the right conditions, conquer disease, prolong life and bring miracles. Nature is of central, MAJOR help and enhances this ability. Cork activates our Bio-field and helps remove blocked or stagnant energy caused by stress in our lives. Disease and pain takes form in the body when these energy blocks have lasted for longer periods of time.</p>\r\n<p>Unsolved blocks and imbalances dissolve when we are working with CREATIVITY and art, which in turn makes it possible for life energy to flow freely through the body again. The whole therapy is based on bringing the energy body to it`s own balance, and from there it is easier to step out of a once painful memory!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>General Objective:</strong><br />Reduce the pollution in the city of Loja and Malacatos Parish in order to promote resources for our Foundation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Specific Objectives:</strong><br>\r\nCarry out an awareness campaign in the city of Loja and Malacatos Parish.<br>\r\nGetting people to practice recycling from the home to the environment.<br>\r\nPutting to good use recyclable materials that many people throw away. <br />\r\nSell our recycled products causing people to contribute to protecting the environment while generating revenue for our Foundation.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>HFANL Language institute</h4>\r\n<p>Our language institute is offered to young people and adults. Ecuador is mostly Spanish-speaking, or native speakers, only the more wealthy and highly educated with access to language education are having access to different education experiences. At the same time it is the poor who bring their vegetables to market, and stand by their rolling stalls on the street corner, are the traders, service providers, etc.and it is usually the poor who meet the tourists in their Business.</p>\r\n<p>The Language institute was established to create equality for all, where everyone has the same opportunity and dignity, regardless of a background.</p>\r\n<p>This is an Education for free to all.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>​Give a Smile to a Child​</h4>\r\n<p>Give a Smile to a Child is an initiative for maintaining several projects which include 200 children. With help from local people, schools and more, we collect clothes, gifts, toys, food and cakes etc for our December visits where we bring gifts, and surprises to 8 schools in the Mountains. Most of all to create a nurturing, caring day for this children on their their free days or Holy Days. <br />December is our biggest priority in this project, not because we go around to spread the Christmas message, but because it is at this time that many children are left alone in the dark and cold weather, especially at a time when many families are struggling to get food and warmth.</p>\r\n<p>Therefore one of our projects in this initiative is our CYCLING PROJECT FOR THE SMILE OF A CHILD.</p>\r\n<p>This project aims to raise funds through cycling in the Parish of Malacatos so that the area becomes familiar with the Hearts Foundation for a New Life which will be providing foster care and protection to children, youth and young pregnant women, single parents, adults, seniors, among others, that somehow are in a social situation of extreme vulnerability. In addition through this endeavor the result will be a beautiful family outing integrating healthy recreation, helping the delivery of aid to be provided to these areas unprotected by society in a healthy way, with LOVE and respect.</p>', '', 1, 2, '2014-06-08 06:44:11', 852, '', '2014-06-13 10:10:15', 852, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-08 06:44:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 5, 6, '', '', 1, 2310, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(11, 78, 'Who is Pearl Shanti?', 'who-is-pearl-shanti', '<h4>Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lioheart are the Founder, ​CEO and the President of Hearts For A New LIFE Foundation</h4>\r\n<p>She is the Author of “Conscious Parenting”, a visionary approach to living with our children, which also will be available in the Spanish language. She cultivates global community through the following Facebook pages: Conscious Parenting, Pure From Within, Holistic Life Style, How To Give Birth as a Goddess, and the group ♥ Let`s Start a Conscious Parenting Movement ♥ as well as her own blog at www.enlightenedchildren.com.</p>\r\n<p>Additionally, she is a regular parenting expert on Selfgrowth.com, USA, the world’s No 1 self-development blog, with more than 1.2 million visits per month, as well as regular parenting contributor for VividLife.me, Canada.</p>\r\n<p>Furthermore she is one of 7 experts who are co-writers of the book “For the Love of our Children”, a book about children with special needs. <a href="http://fortheloveofourchildren.com/ebook.html">www.fortheloveofourchildren.com/ebook.html</a></p>\r\n<p>Pearl Shanti writes contributing articles for several alternative magazines in Norway and in other countries.<br />She has been interviewed by major newspapers in Norway and been a guest at national and international radio shows.</p>\r\n<p>She presently lives a holistic life style in the valley of longevity, Vilcabamba, Ecuador - with home school for her son Leopold. Pearl Shanti is psychic and has seen other dimensions her whole life.</p>\r\n<p>After being a successful business woman for several years, she gave this up in order to go deeper into the spiritual world she had been seeing since childhood.</p>\r\n<p>Pearl Shanti is a Reiki Grand Master, healer, re-birther, heart opener, animal whisperer, nutrition consultant, Feng Shui advisor, herbal specialist, author, coach, philosopher, metaphysician, French Gourmet Chef, children listener, artist, workshop facilitator, The Melchizedek Method facilitator, raw food specialist and life alchemist and most of all mother for 3 lovely children, and grandmother for 3 beautiful boys.</p>\r\n<p>She has been a healer for more than 30 years, had her own healing center and ashram – and she is an expert on survival skills and living from Mother Nature`s resources for several years in the deep forests in Norway.</p>\r\n<p>She has been living on prana/light and knows that everyone decides how many years they want to stay in their physical body and that death is an illusion.</p>\r\n<p>Pearl Shanti has been wanderer on this planet. She has lived in Norway, Spain, India, Nepal, Sri Lanka, England and now Ecuador, in the Andes. This youthful grandmother has lived in ashrams in India and found a previous lifetime in Spain. She has climbed Mount Kailash, met wild elephants in the jungle in Southern-India and bathed in the holy Ganges.</p>\r\n<p>Moreover she practices yoga, pranah yoga, karma yoga, meditation and study The Law of Attraction. Pearl Shanti focuses on building good karma and to living a conscious lifestyle in a natural way with pure simplicity.</p>\r\n<p>With her big heart she has been helping people all over the world, and she has consciously incarnated here on earth to share from her deep selfless wisdom.</p>\r\n<p>The children in the world, including her own, are her passion - and her vision is to improve the conditions for children by inspiring others to become MORE Conscious Parents.<br />The children are the greatest treasures on earth - and it is her purpose to help parents support their children to bring forth their highest potential, to be happy and healthy.<br />Her philosophy is that ALL the children on this beautiful planet are our responsibility – not just our own kids.</p>\r\n<p>Pearl Shanti`s calmness and tolerance makes it easy for children to confide in her- they know that she can see them for who they truly are. When working for the school Nature Kids in England, these abilities were especially useful.</p>\r\n<p>For Pearl parenting is a blessing and a gift when we regard life as a joy, not a struggle.<br />Her experiences in her own life have shown that conscious parenting works.</p>\r\n<p>She is here to serve in a truthful and humble way. Moreover her desire is to help motivate parents in improving their lives, to assist families to manage their lives with harmony, LOVE, health and spiritual growth.</p>\r\n<p>All parents do the best they know how. Pearl Shanti is not here to promote “superior” parenting or lofty ideals. She simply wants to inspire parents to become more conscious and find solutions that work.</p>\r\n<p>Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lionheart is a way-shower in the new parenting paradigm, guiding parents all over the world in her most important “call” from her heart. The new parenting paradigm will create a new world as One Family, and it is our task as parents to become the change we want to see in the world.</p>\r\n<p>In her own words:</p>\r\n<p>"We, the parents, are the children''s future and hope. We are the change, and changes can happen quickly if we work together. We ALL do the best WE KNOW HOW.<br />There’s always more to learn that will make us even better at what we do! But it''s not about what we could have done, should have done, or what we continue to do, but about what we are able to do now and CHOOSE TO DO NOW WITH WHAT WE NOW KNOW! There are never problems, only tasks to be solved."</p>\r\n<p>And by her gentle guidance many parents will eventually see the solutions in their own life as well as in their relationships with their children.</p>\r\n<p>Learn more about Pearl on Facebook as well as her own blog:</p>\r\n<p><br /><a href="https://www.facebook.com/PearlShantiLodurLionheartHappyCrazyAndMe">www.facebook.com/PearlShantiLodurLionheartHappyCrazyAndMe</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.enlightenedchildren.com">www.enlightenedchildren.com</a></p>\r\n<p>Pearl Shanti is an International Author, Visionary Partner, Director of Children''s Publications and Cookbook Publications with The Hive Publications<br />Learn more about her publishing work at:</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.thehivepublications.com/meet-the-authors-and-contributors.html">http://www.thehivepublications.com/meet-the-authors-and-contributors.html</a></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>​ Pearl`s Blog​</h4>\r\n<p>Enlightened Children is Pearl''s blog where she focuses on child development, brain research, conscious parenting and how you can unleash the genius in your child. Here you will find articles, news, information and valuable content that will help you help your children reach their highest potential. Pearl Shanti´s heartfelt message is to share about ALL children´s true potential. Within every child there is a genius! All babies are super intelligent, and when they are surrounded by LOVE, understanding, patience and conscious parenting, they will remain so for the rest of their lives! Every child is born with total consciousness, and they are Humanity''s greatest gift ! They are here to show us a brand new world, if we let them. Pearl Shanti LOVES to share what she has experienced, because she knows it works. Her goal is to be a Messenger of Love &amp; Peace. Read more about her work at <a href="http://www.enlightenedchildren.com">www.enlightenedchildren.com</a><a href="http://enlightenedchildren.com/"></a></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>​The Inca Spirit ​M​agazin​e​</h4>\r\n<p>This periodical owned by Ms. Pearl Lodur-Lionheart is an innovative and informative magazine with a human touch, full of LOVE in order to educate society about culture and Holistic Life Style. The long-term intent is that the magazine will transmit a legacy to future generations, which will have an effect on not only economic, but also individual well-being. The proceeds from this publication will be spent on social welfare of children, single mothers and elderly people.</p>\r\n<p>Its main purpose is to convey what it truly means a natural holistic living to be aware of what nature gives us. It asks us in our daily lives to consider what may be the legacy we leave to our children if we do not start with ourselves in nurturing our world. The goal of this publication is to cultivate a world full of tranquility, peace a more harmonious life.</p>\r\n<p>For a small donation the online edition is available for download.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Pearl`s Heart Factory</h4>\r\n<p>This is the production project of Hearts For a New Life Foundation, creating Pure Therapy Products. Pearl''s Heart Factory creates Paper Art Items, Ecologic Personal Care Towels for Women and much more. Visit the Shop for the current selection of products.</p>\r\n<p><br />The Heart factory is also a Therapy and Training model, a helping hand to "HELP to SELF help" for the women who need therapy from "Mother Pearl´s Home". This is an educational offer from Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lionheart, to help them take control over their own life, with work, food, accommodation and education to what they really want out of LIFE- A START OVER ...</p>\r\n<p>Pearl´s Heart Factory provides hands on education and training to take responsibility of their own LIFE and Children. The project is to help these girls, the young mothers and their children to become self sufficient, to make responsible choices and guide their children in a conscious upbringing, where LOVE, knowledge and a healthy economy will be important. Helping is not about distributing money, but to giving others the feeling that they themselves have created their income. Here they will learn to create a better life for their little family.  They will work in the factory, aiding Pearl Shanti in helping children and their parents all over the world. Together we will be helping children in the world who really need us, not only here in Ecuador.</p>\r\n<p>The workers will be able to develop ideas and offer suggestions, they will be rewarded when their ideas and suggestions are implemented in the production. This will increase their self-esteem. Their proposals will not only be used as a product, but looked further into as well, to see if it would be possible for the employer to start her own business in her own location, and the worker will be personally coached by Pearl Shanti in many ways to manifest their creative idea, becoming able to patent their own idea/product.</p>\r\n<p>At the same time Pearl Shanti supports poor local farmers by purchasing materials needed for products from them, such as yarn for weaving, wood materials, dried coconut fibres for woodcarving, metals like silver bells etc, pottery items on order, glass production, seaming and other related services which would be useful for the factory.<br /> <br />The policy of "Hearts For A new LIFE" is to never hand the money out to the woman, but to give dignity so they can learn to work for their own money.  This is Pearl Shanti''s vision behind the factory in addition to the Foundation. This is a company which will support – when it is financially settled, giving 50 % of the profits to secure as much as possible the areas of the rainforest from further destruction. This will be the long-term purpose and benefit of the workers of the factory. The factory is not a production line but a full training and therapeutic program and work place for young single mothers who has had a rough start in life.</p>\r\n<p>This will give woman a choice to have paid work and to be employers of the factory, with the knowlege that they are working for a good cause,where they are helping the rainforest. This will support the young mothers, heal their place in the community, their confidence and vital self respect – as well as giving the workers a quality life and a happy heart. Every product in the factory will be made from natural fabric (not from the rain forest).</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>​​Pearl´s Space<br />​</h4>\r\n<p>"The Hive Publications" ​/​Pearls Books ​ and more​ which also is connected with the shop too</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.thehivepublications.com/the-hive-bookstore.html">www.thehivepublications.com/the-hive-bookstore.html</a></p>', '', 1, 2, '2014-06-08 06:56:45', 852, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-08 06:56:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 1, 5, '', '', 1, 1917, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(12, 79, 'Support & Sponsors', 'support-sponsors', '<h4>Design, Hosting &amp; Sponsor</h4>\r\n<p>Henning Byø<br />Phone: +45 28 15 89 19<br /><a href="mailto:henning@littlemonkeydesign.com">henning@littlemonkeydesign.com</a><br>\r\n<a href="http://www.littlemonkeydesign.com" target="_blank">www.littlemonkeydesign.com</a><br>\r\n<a href="http://www.cmsreadycloud.com" target="_blank">www.cmsreadycloud.com</a></p><br>\r\n<h4>Photos</h4>\r\n<p>Roberto Melendez&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Roberto Melendez Enlighten Photo gallery<br>\r\n<a href="https://www.facebook.com/RobertoMelendezEnlightenPhotogallery" target="_blank">www.facebook.com/RobertoMelendezEnlightenPhotogallery</a></p><br>\r\n<h4>The Hive Publications</h4>\r\n<p><a href="mailto:thehivepublications@gmail.com">thehivepublications@gmail.com</a><br /><a href="http://www.TheHivePublications.com" target="_blank">www.TheHivePublications.com</a><br><a href="http://www.TheHivePublications.com" target="_blank">ONE Legacy Works, Inc.</a></p>', '', 0, 2, '2014-06-08 07:06:45', 852, '', '2014-06-08 07:10:45', 852, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-08 07:06:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"