(13, 81, 'Terms of use', 'terms-of-use', '<p>No part of this site or publications may be reproduced, stored in any retrieval system, or transmitted in any form or by any means - electronic, mechanical, photocopying, recording, or otherwise - without the written permission of Pearl Shanti Lodur Lionheart.</p>\r\n<p>The information, consultation services and presentations offered here are used for guidance, social awareness, personal education and can be powerful life-changing tools. This information however is not intended to be a substitute for medical care.</p>\r\n<p>Neither Pearl Shanti Lodur Lionheart, <a href="http://www.EnlightenedChildren.com">www.EnlightenedChildren.com</a>, Hearts For a New Life Foundation, The Hive Publications, nor One Legacy Works Inc. assumes responsibility for your improper use of the contents offered.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Disclaimer</h4>\r\n<p>Every effort has been made to ensure accuracy of information. As with any associated links and content, some may require updating. If you find any such information which requires refreshing we invite you to notify us in writing and all necessary adjustments will be made.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Copyright</h4>\r\n<p>Hearts For A New LIFE Foundation All rights reserved. For all texts, Private photos &amp; Photos from Roberto Melendez and other intellectual property on our website applies to copyright and other laws protecting intellectual property. Use, especially copying and distribution of protected content, even if it only applies to a single intellectual property, is expressly prohibited unless prior written consent is obtained. The same applies to public reproduction for commercial purposes.</p>', '', 1, 2, '2014-06-08 11:38:03', 852, '', '2014-06-08 18:35:07', 852, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-08 11:38:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","i