(14, 83, 'Become a ​Volunteer', 'become-a-volunteer', '<h4>Do you want a year off ? Do you speak Spanish or wish to learn Spanish&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<p>The Norwegian "Hearts For A New Life Foundation" is an international organization helping sexually abused children and young women in Ecuador. We have just taken over very big and wonderful housing facilities which we will fully utilize as a therapeutic institution. The institution is situated in a peaceful place in the Andes mountains - with a wonderful view of the surrounding mountains and nature. We are on the warm side - towards the Amazon Jungle. With a year around summer temperature.</p>\r\n<p>We require volunteers for the institution from this autumn.The home for women and children will be ready for commencement no later than December 1 st 2014. We provide food and lodging - and you will live in very pleasant surroundings. This volunteer work will give you your Visa for 1 year (normally it is only 3 months) with a possibility for renewal. You will be given a legalized certificate when the volunteer-period is ended, which will be beneficial for various future educational paths.</p>\r\n<p><a href="index.php?option=com_alfcontact&amp;view=alfcontact&amp;Itemid=115">Contact us</a></p>', '', 0, 2, '2014-06-09 12:19:01', 852, '', '2014-06-09 12:22:45', 852, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-09 12:19:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigatio