(15, 84, 'Donate', 'donate', '<p>Hearts for a New Life foundation" directed by Pearl Shanti, is a nonprofit organization recognized internationally for its successful, high impact social campaigns of assistance to the most vulnerable members of society.</p>\r\n<p>Currently, the program is promoting ''''Da Dignity – Give Dignity" an initiative in the city of Loja, located in southern Ecuador. This program provides not only financial support but also free services in health, education, legal counseling, training in productive life skills, family planning, alcoholism, self esteem, among other social issues affecting the local community.</p>\r\n<p>We invite you to join the community of sponsors of this program. Your help is critical to improving the quality of life of people living in extreme poverty and away from the most basic resources to address their situation. The time to take action is now. In the time it takes to finish reading this article, chances are that a life is being lost. Your contribution can be the vital difference that helps a young person win their battle.</p>\r\n<h4>MAKE a ​Donation​</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Org. Reg. Norway: 911 849 119<br>\r\nCultura Bank Norway:  1254.05.90131</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Org. Reg. Ecuador: 1191750035001<br>\r\nBanco ProCredit Ecuador: 26-0101-162346-0</p>', '', 0, 2, '2014-06-09 12:26:01', 852, '', '2015-01-29 19:37:55', 852, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-09 12:26:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_m