(16, 85, 'Hidden', 'hidden', '<p>She is 13 years old, tears are running down her cheeks, she wears a painful silence. She has just found out that she, by force is pregnant, a child brings forth a child, the unborn child''s father is her own father. How could she tell, and to whom?</p>', '', 1, 9, '2014-06-25 16:21:57', 852, '', '2014-06-25 16:23:13', 852, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-25 16:21:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 6, '', '', 1, 18, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(17, 86, 'Hidden', 'hidden2', '<p>Together with her mother she just come out of the police station, she is 11 years old and constantly raped by her brother, who brings the family financial support. Instead of pressing charges, she received an appointment for a free pregnancy prevention injection. She is forced to accept, no one will protect her.</p>', '', 1, 9, '2014-06-25 16:24:10', 852, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-25 16:24:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 1, 1, '', '', 1, 20, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(18, 87, 'Pearl', 'pearl', '<p>She is only 8 years old, she stopped talking seven months ago, no one knows why she does not talk any more, only she does, but she will not tell on her own family member.</p>\r\n<p>Is it Normal for A child to be : afraid alone forced rejected hated raped beaten abused</p>\r\n<p>Do you know what my greatest wish is, she whispered? No, I said.......all though I knew her answer. She replayed : I wish for the night when I can venture to sleep.</p>', '', 1, 9, '2014-06-25 16:24:25', 852, '', '2014-06-25 16:33:53', 852, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-06-25 16:24:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 0, '', '', 1, 22, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', '');

