(64, 6, 1, '', '2014-06-06 14:28:16', 852, 5587, '76dff66acf5f642053b15f94926308a7b29dd238', '{"id":6,"asset_id":"67","title":"Secret","alias":"john-nelson-2","introtext":"<p><span style=\\"color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\\">This post contains heartbreaking pain and may be challenging for some .... Read carefully,with an open mind and HEART and send your LOVE to those I write about. Please do not judge any one in my sharing,send your LOVE to all who are involved. The \\"Painful Silence\\" is a series of true stories,told by souls who did not give up their hope of a NEW beginning!!!<\\/span><br style=\\"color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\\" \\/><span style=\\"color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\\">This is another deep and he<\\/span><span class=\\"text_exposed_show\\" style=\\"display: inline; color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;\\">artbreaking sharing,told to me by a very young girl. This is why I came into their life''s - to do something to help - open your heart and tune in to their happiness of CHANGE .<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\"She can hear the beat of her own pulse...The moist night is dark and cold. She squeezes her teeth together, while the tears are coming more and more. Suddenly she is alone and abandoned - the empty silence is all she can hear. She notices the pain from the beatings and kicks, the pain is unbearable. Her clothes are brutally torn off - she is left there- naked.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The hard concrete floor feels like knives of ice, penetrating the wounds, the warm blood suddenly becomes a cold and enveloping cloak.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>She can still smell his breath, filled with alcohol and tobacco.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Her body is wincing, as she hears the whining from her newborn, who - like his three older siblings, was conceived the same way.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fearing what the children will see or hear, she stopped screaming when child number two was born. She chose to receive beatings and kicks, allowing the rape go on in silence, to protect the little ones.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>She is a very young woman, not even 20 years old.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>She is convinced that she is to blame, that the violence is justified.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The first abuse happened six years ago, when she was a guest in a family party. The family had invited the man, she believed that she could trust the guests there, but she was taken advantage of in the backyard, while the other guests were dancing to the loud music, the music blocked her cries for help.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The party ended abruptly when she came crawling, begging for help. She was 13 years old, only a child. She clung to her mother, but was dismissed with loathing.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Her family forced her to marry the assaulter when it turned out that she was pregnant. They turned their back to her after the marriage ceremony.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>She was only a child herself, and now she is the mother of 4 children, who she constantly tries to protect. She is not the only one who is kicked and beaten. Yet - she asks her husband to beat her, instead of the children.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Every night she is praying, with tears in her eyes. She asks for help - for herself and the children. What kind of life is this ?, she asks herself.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Don`t we deserve better ?<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Shaking from cold and pain she falls asleep, fearing for the life of her children and herself.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In her dreams she hears a voice, filled with peace and love:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\" Yes, my child, you deserve the very best, help is on the way, you need not live this way ! \\"<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>With a deep longing in her heart, she sleeps with the newborn in her arms, and though the fear almost tears her apart, she knows at the same time that new opportunities are on the way!&nbsp;<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"9","created":"2014-06-01 17:58:13","created_by":"852","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-06-06 14:28:16","modified_by":"852","checked_out":"852","checked_out_time":"2014-06-06 14:27:42","publish_up":"2014-06-01 17:58:13","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":4,"ordering":"0","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"0","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
