(79, 9, 1, '', '2014-06-08 06:07:37', 852, 4565, '0d5fe07624dffd6e1cdb1e3cf7337a7ea706d286', '{"id":9,"asset_id":75,"title":"What is \\"Hearts for a New LIFE\\"","alias":"what-is-hearts-for-a-new-life","introtext":"<h4>\\"Hearts for a New Life Foundation\\"<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Our mission is the achievement of integrated development of girls and children from economically disadvantaged backgrounds as well as that of parents and single mothers. We accomplish this through an education of quality and just treatment with lifestyle solutions and skills; respecting their rights, their diversity, their natural rhythm of growth and learning with a constant concern for the environment they live in; developing fundamental values integrating the family and community. We endeavor to support \\u200b in all these ways at the beginning stages of a new life, a life which can be filled with peace and happiness!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This is most of all an Association for Young Mothers, but to help simply the individual is not enough. We believe to create lasting change in an often hostile setting, we must be prepared to help to heal the whole family.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This is an Establishment for a NEW Beginning and a Conscious Upbringing.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>There is a vital need for support of young and single mothers in South America. Young girls are frequently forced to marry if they become pregnant with a child, often even if the pregnancy is a result of sexual abuse. Many young girls experience abuse by family members. Many run away from rape and incest and hide in the mountains.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>HFANL is here to help the young mothers and their children. We support them in a caring way with LOVE, education, food, shelter, medical care, support with needed legal action, therapy, paid work, and so much more. We help them to create a new start and a new life, the LIFE that they wish for themselves.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>First of ALL this is a powerful work of conveying FEELINGS\\u2026 the feeling of the DIGNITY OF LIFE, the feeling of being LOVED, cared for, appreciated and for my Team and I to GIVE them back the feeling of LIFE! Their OWN LIFE!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We help the young mothers to feel responsible for their children''s lives, to LOVE their children, even after their painful experiences. The main philosophy of the association is to train them to help themselves - to empower young single mothers to be able to take responsibility for their own and their children''s lives and provide for their families and futures.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4><br \\/>General Information<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Not everyone has the same opportunities to live a quality LIFE. Some never do, unless someone comes with a BIG warm Heart and an outstretched Hand, sharing insights on how to free themselves from a painful past to live a more worthwhile LIFE. This is why Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lionheart is the creator of Hearts For a New LIFE Foundation. Welcome to our site! We wish this work to INSPIRE and uplift YOU! This is an inclusive place with immense motivation where there is room for EVERY ONE who wishes to change their LIFE to the LIFE they want to Create!<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"2","created":"2014-06-08 06:07:37","created_by":"852","created_by_alias":"","modified":"","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2014-06-08 06:07:37","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ordering":null,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":null,"metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(80, 1, 1, '', '2014-06-08 06:13:00', 852, 4071, '5f3ef48d462fc6a0a87d332a767f340c0f388421', '{"id":1,"asset_id":"54","title":"Heart for a new life","alias":"heart-for-a-new-life","introtext":"<p>\\"I am a giver of LOVE and I LOVE to give a helping hand that leads to a better LIFE... I am a children''s lawyer and this is my work internationally.. This is my message to the world, my work, web pages, articles, radio shows and books. In our world, there is enough for everyone, it''s all about being there for our fellow man. Anyone can fall down in the dust, that does not mean we who have the resources are going to ignore them and let them remain there, it''s against my nature, heart, and compassionate LOVE to ignore a soul in need ... Nothing in any possible way, can please me more than to see the joy in the eyes of the one who receives my help, so I know this is my Heartfelt Passion as I am compelled toward the BLISS* of Giving my outstretched hand of LOVE and understanding to ONE and ALL!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I am a Teacher of Advanced Spiritual Metaphysics, who offer and are manifesting permanent states of Harmonic Consciousness for women and children all over the world. I am a \\"Path Opener\\", A Visionary, Mentor, Author, Speaker and the Usher of change. My compassion and deep unconditional LOVE for humanity and all of LIFE, are my only ONE Goal. As the truth seeker I AM. I have chosen to venture to the very core of consciousness itself... Purest Clarity of this is felt in me of such a Deep Heart vibration, that only LOVE is my Language, and my heart is The LOVE transformer.. I am here to make sure that these precious souls will blossom into their full essence as we all collectively transition into our own true worth. I have a depth of awareness and expanse of clarity that makes my life an example for others.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I accept all who cross my path at their chosen stage of life and offer an open heart for those who are ready to immerse themselves in their own living mastery. It is ALL about \\u2665Simplicity\\u2665Honesty\\u2665LOVE\\u2665 !!! My Life, My Perspective, My Attitude about everything is very simple.. I Am here to serve in pure LOVE which is my only KEY* and intention! \\"You just know when you''ve helped someone, then your heart hums in purest JOY, then you can feel the Peace in their Heart and see it when you look into their Smiling Eyes!\\"<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Founder and President&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lionheart \\u2665<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"2","created":"2014-06-01 16:00:49","created_by":"852","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-06-08 06:13:00","modified_by":"852","checked_out":"852","checked_out_time":"2014-06-08 06:12:34","publish_up":"2014-06-01 16:00:49","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/ps.jpg\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"left\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"images\\\\\\/ps.jpg\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"left\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":15,"ordering":"1","metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":"56","metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"1","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0),
(81, 10, 1, '', '2014-06-08 06:44:11', 852, 8982, '32725b24961d0ab2cd3e8f5f9d39c0b3446250cd', '{"id":10,"asset_id":77,"title":"Projects","alias":"projects","introtext":"<h4>Mother Pearl\\u00b4s Home<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>This project is aimed at social support in which institutional care for children, youth, pregnant women, single mothers, adults and older at risk adults, disadvantaged and\\/or abandoned individuals is offered exclusive priority, ensuring their protection and the defense of their rights. At Mother Pearl''s Home we always seek reintegration back into the family unit and the preservation of community. <br \\/>This work is located at \\"MOTHER PEARL''S HOME\\" in Malacatos, in the Parish of the Hearts for a new life Foundation led by its President Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lionheart of Norwegian nationality. Gifted with LOVE and limitless charisma, Pearl is able to carry out this work with the sole purpose of helping vulnerable people in society, This assistance will be provided in a home group setting, supported financially by the Foundation and by both local and foreign volunteers from around the world.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4>\\u200bYunanga \\u200bCorazon Cultural<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Project Yunanga \\u200bCorazon Cultural is our Educational offer for the poor Children of Malacatos who are not able to afford travel to the city of Loja for an education. This project is intended to promote and secure access to learning Music, Art, Culture, Nutrition, Color, Natural Medicine, Yoga, Meditation and more in the Parish of Malacatos Loja City. Yunanga \\u200bCorazon Cultural is there for this sector of society educating the children in a way that is believed to be necessary for the growth and strengthening of values \\u200b\\u200band morals through learning the arts instructing them with the affection and care that children deserve.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This project will take place in the Yunanga Hosteria in which we currently hold guitar lessons directed to children of Malacatos and surroundings, whose owner is Lord Nelson Medina, generously offering his beautiful property for this project.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br \\/>\\"Hearts Foundation for A New Life\\" led by its President Ms. Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lionheart, who with her wonderful gifts of knowledge and charisma intends this assistance to be provided for these vulnerable and neglected members of society. It is Ms Pearl''s Personal and Team Vision that by running this project to build a foundation for future young artists and good people full of affection and love to enrich society and as a result, also the country at large.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4>Recycling - Therapy and Art!<br \\/>Love the World<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Some of the most wonderful things that this foundation focuses on lie in the activities in which the HFANL community transforms recycled items into ART! This project mostly reaches the Children in order create awareness, protect nature and to instill a creative intelligence and responsibility in young people. For example, working with cork is a soothing form of therapy, it is a natural, soft material giving an indescribable inner calm. <br \\/>One of the forms of therapy at \\"Mother Pearl''s Home\\" is recycling. Beginning with January 2015 we will start our project of transforming waste into the finest art as our Special Therapy. Working with wine corks is a great therapy for our patients, and especially for those patients who carry the negative memories associated with alcohol from their own childhood, abuse memories or being mistreated somehow when alcohol was involved . Pearl''s therapy method transforms trash (trauma and painful memories) into beautiful art and joy (liberation) - a NEW LIFE and a chance to start over. It''s about collaboration with the natural material of cork, and the human body . We will be working on many different Recycled projects such as Paper, glass bottles, water bottles and more.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The greatest miracle on earth is our body. It contains infinite wisdom and vast resources that can, given the right conditions, conquer disease, prolong life and bring miracles. Nature is of central, MAJOR help and enhances this ability. Cork activates our Bio-field and helps remove blocked or stagnant energy caused by stress in our lives. Disease and pain takes form in the body when these energy blocks have lasted for longer periods of time.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Unsolved blocks and imbalances dissolve when we are working with CREATIVITY and art, which in turn makes it possible for life energy to flow freely through the body again. The whole therapy is based on bringing the energy body to it`s own balance, and from there it is easier to step out of a once painful memory!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>General Objective: <br \\/>Reduce the pollution in the city of Loja and Malacatos Parish in order to promote resources for our Foundation. <br \\/>Specific Objectives:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Carry out an awareness campaign in the city of Loja and Malacatos Parish. <br \\/>Getting people to practice recycling from the home to the environment. <br \\/>Putting to good use recyclable materials that many people throw away. <br \\/>Sell our recycled products causing people to contribute to protecting the environment while generating revenue for our Foundation.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4>HFANL Language institute<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Our language institute is offered to young people and adults. Ecuador is mostly Spanish-speaking, or native speakers, only the more wealthy and highly educated with access to language education are having access to different education experiences. At the same time it is the poor who bring their vegetables to market, and stand by their rolling stalls on the street corner, are the traders, service providers, etc.and it is usually the poor who meet the tourists in their Business.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Language institute was established to create equality for all, where everyone has the same opportunity and dignity, regardless of a background.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This is an Education for free to all.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<h4>\\u200bGive a Smile to a Child\\u200b<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p>Give a Smile to a Child is an initiative for maintaining several projects which include 200 children. With help from local people, schools and more, we collect clothes, gifts, toys, food and cakes etc for our December visits where we bring gifts, and surprises to 8 schools in the Mountains. Most of all to create a nurturing, caring day for this children on their their free days or Holy Days. <br \\/>December is our biggest priority in this project, not because we go around to spread the Christmas message, but because it is at this time that many children are left alone in the dark and cold weather, especially at a time when many families are struggling to get food and warmth.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Therefore one of our projects in this initiative is our CYCLING PROJECT FOR THE SMILE OF A CHILD.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This project aims to raise funds through cycling in the Parish of Malacatos so that the area becomes familiar with the Hearts Foundation for a New Life which will be providing foster care and protection to children, youth and young pregnant women, single parents, adults, seniors, among others, that somehow are in a social situation of extreme vulnerability. In addition through this endeavor the result will be a beautiful family outing integrating healthy recreation, helping the delivery of aid to be provided to these areas unprotected by society in a healthy way, with LOVE and respect.<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"2","created":"2014-06-08 06:44:11","created_by":"852","created_by_alias":"","modified":"","modified_by":null,"checked_out":null,"checked_out_time":null,"publish_up":"2014-06-08 06:44:11","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"alternative_readmore\\":\\"\\",\\"article_layout\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publishing_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_article_options\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_backend\\":\\"\\",\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\":\\"\\"}","version":1,"ordering":null,"metakey":"","metadesc":"","access":"1","hits":null,"metadata":"{\\"robots\\":\\"\\",\\"author\\":\\"\\",\\"rights\\":\\"\\",\\"xreference\\":\\"\\"}","featured":"0","language":"*","xreference":""}', 0);
