(104, 1, 1, '', '2014-06-09 12:38:32', 852, 5699, '0b6c7825cbe8e050289b1649f989c4de84b07152', '{"id":1,"asset_id":"54","title":"Heart for a new life","alias":"heart-for-a-new-life","introtext":"<p>\\"I am a giver of LOVE and I LOVE to give a helping hand that leads to a better LIFE... I am a children''s lawyer and this is my work internationally.. This is my message to the world, my work, web pages, articles, radio shows and books. In our world, there is enough for everyone, it''s all about being there for our fellow man. Anyone can fall down in the dust, that does not mean we who have the resources are going to ignore them and let them remain there, it''s against my nature, heart, and compassionate LOVE to ignore a soul in need ... Nothing in any possible way, can please me more than to see the joy in the eyes of the one who receives my help, so I know this is my Heartfelt Passion as I am compelled toward the BLISS* of Giving my outstretched hand of LOVE and understanding to ONE and ALL!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I am a Teacher of Advanced Spiritual Metaphysics, who offer and are manifesting permanent states of Harmonic Consciousness for women and children all over the world. I am a \\"Path Opener\\", A Visionary, Mentor, Author, Speaker and the Usher of change. My compassion and deep unconditional LOVE for humanity and all of LIFE, are my only ONE Goal. As the truth seeker I AM. I have chosen to venture to the very core of consciousness itself... Purest Clarity of this is felt in me of such a Deep Heart vibration, that only LOVE is my Language, and my heart is The LOVE transformer.. I am here to make sure that these precious souls will blossom into their full essence as we all collectively transition into our own true worth. I have a depth of awareness and expanse of clarity that makes my life an example for others.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I accept all who cross my path at their chosen stage of life and offer an open heart for those who are ready to immerse themselves in their own livi