(116, 1, 1, '', '2014-07-29 08:05:17', 852, 5713, '51a56467155cb5cf9dc1c87a2e8c9f72566de498', '{"id":1,"asset_id":"54","title":"Heart for a new life","alias":"heart-for-a-new-life","introtext":"<p>\\"I am a giver of LOVE and I LOVE to give a helping hand that leads to a better LIFE... I am a children''s lawyer and this is my work internationally.. This is my message to the world, my work, web pages, articles, radio shows and books. In our world, there is enough for everyone, it''s all about being there for our fellow man. Anyone can fall down in the dust, that does not mean we who have the resources are going to ignore them and let them remain there, it''s against my nature, heart, and compassionate LOVE to ignore a soul in need ... Nothing in any possible way, can please me more than to see the joy in the eyes of the one who receives my help, so I know this is my Heartfelt Passion as I am compelled toward the BLISS* of Giving my outstretched hand of LOVE and understanding to ONE and ALL!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I am a Teacher of Advanced Spiritual Metaphysics, who offer and are manifesting permanent states of Harmonic Consciousness for women and children all over the world. I am a \\"Path Opener\\", A Visionary, Mentor, Author, Speaker and the Usher of change. My compassion and deep unconditional LOVE for humanity and all of LIFE, are my only ONE Goal. As the truth seeker I AM. I have chosen to venture to the very core of consciousness itself... Purest Clarity of this is felt in me of such a Deep Heart vibration, that only LOVE is my Language, and my heart is The LOVE transformer.. I am here to make sure that these precious souls will blossom into their full essence as we all collectively transition into our own true worth. I have a depth of awareness and expanse of clarity that makes my life an example for others.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I accept all who cross my path at their chosen stage of life and offer an open heart for those who are ready to immerse themselves in their own living mastery. It is ALL about \\u2665Simplicity\\u2665Honesty\\u2665LOVE\\u2665 !!! My Life, My Perspective, My Attitude about everything is very simple.. I Am here to serve in pure LOVE which is my only KEY* and intention! \\"You just know when you''ve helped someone, then your heart hums in purest JOY, then you can feel the Peace in their Heart and see it when you look into their Smiling Eyes!\\"<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Founder and President&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;Pearl Shanti Lodur-Lionheart \\u2665<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<form action=\\"https:\\/\\/www.paypal.com\\/cgi-bin\\/webscr\\" method=\\"post\\" target=\\"_top\\">\\r\\n<input type=\\"hidden\\" name=\\"cmd\\" value=\\"_s-xclick\\">\\r\\n<input type=\\"hidden\\" name=\\"hosted_button_id\\" value=\\"VSP5M5ETD8PKL\\">\\r\\n<input type=\\"image\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/www.paypalobjects.com\\/en_US\\/i\\/btn\\/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\\" border=\\"0\\" name=\\"submit\\" alt=\\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\\">\\r\\n<img alt=\\"\\" border=\\"0\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/www.paypalobjects.com\\/en_US\\/i\\/scr\\/pixel.gif\\" width=\\"1\\" height=\\"1\\">\\r\\n<\\/form>\\r\\n<p>\\"Hearts for a New Life foundation\\" directed by Pearl Shanti, is a nonprofit organization recognized internationally for its successful, high impact social campaigns of assistance to the most vulnerable members of society.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Currently, the program is promoting ''''Da Dignity \\u2013 Give Dignity\\" an initiative in the city of Loja, located in southern Ecuador. This program provides not only financial support but also free services in health, education, legal counseling, training in productive life skills, family planning, alcoholism, self esteem, among other social issues affecting the local community.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We invite you to join the community of sponsors of this program. Your help is critical to improving the quality of life of people living in extreme poverty and away